1. Create Words
    -Assign difficulty, meaning, use cases, etc.

2. Create Flash Cards 
    -Includes above details of each word.

3. Create Box Structure 
    - Can be done using Arrays or Database Tables.

4. Create Learning Algorithm
    -All start from New at start.
    -Move Up if correct, Down if Wrong.
    -Include Reviewing at appropriate intervals.

5. Create Database Structure
    -Store user progress and stats in database

